                    <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-code-branch"></i> Build Track & Source Track</h2>
                    
                    <div class="track-grid">
                        <div class="track-card build" id="build-track">
                            <h3><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Build Track</h3>
                            <p><strong>Level:</strong> L0 - L3</p>
                            <p>Build Track menggunakan provenance sebagai "receipt" untuk build software Anda. Menjawab tiga pertanyaan kritis :</p>
                            <ul style="margin: 1rem 0 1rem 1.5rem;">
                                <li><strong>Identity of the builder</strong> - Siapa yang membangun?</li>
                                <li><strong>Build process used</strong> - Bagaimana dibangun?</li>
                                <li><strong>Inputs used</strong> - Material apa yang digunakan?</li>
                            </ul>
                            
                            <h4 style="margin-top: 1rem;">Level Build Track:</h4>
                            <ul style="margin: 0.5rem 0 0 1.5rem;">
                                <li><strong>L0</strong>: No guarantees</li>
                                <li><strong>L1</strong>: Provenance exists (mencegah kesalahan)</li>
                                <li><strong>L2</strong>: Hosted build platform (authenticated provenance)</li>
                                <li><strong>L3</strong>: Hardened builds (isolasi kuat, tamper protection)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="track-card source" id="source-track">
                            <h3><i class="fas fa-code"></i> Source Track</h3>
                            <p><strong>Level:</strong> L1 - L4</p>
                            <p>Source Track menjawab "Bagaimana kita tahu source code ini sesuai dengan yang diinginkan organisasi?" Fokus pada change management process .</p>
                            
                            <h4 style="margin-top: 1rem;">Level Source Track:</h4>
                            <ul style="margin: 0.5rem 0 0 1.5rem;">
                                <li><strong>L1</strong>: Version controlled (foundation)</li>
                                <li><strong>L2</strong>: Source attestations and controls</li>
                                <li><strong>L3</strong>: Protected references with continuous enforcement</li>
                                <li><strong>L4</strong>: Two-party review (gold standard untuk production code)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
