                <section id="provenance">
                    <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-file-signature"></i> Provenance</h2>
                    
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Apa itu Provenance?</h3>
                        <p>Provenance adalah metadata tentang bagaimana suatu artifact dibuat, termasuk proses build, top-level source, dan dependencies. Mengetahui provenance memungkinkan konsumen software membuat keputusan keamanan berbasis risiko .</p>
                        
                        <div class="code-container">
                            <div class="code-header">
                                <span>Contoh Provenance Format (JSON)</span>
                                <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)"><i class="fas fa-copy"></i> Copy</button>
                            </div>
                            <pre><code class="language-json">
{
  "_type": "https://in-toto.io/Statement/v0.1",
  "subject": [{"name": "_", "digest": {"sha256": "..."}}],
  "predicateType": "https://slsa.dev/provenance/v0.2",
  "predicate": {
    "builder": { "id": "https://github.com/slsa-framework/slsa-github-generator/.github/workflows/generator_generic_slsa3.yml@refs/tags/v1.5.0" },
    "buildType": "https://github.com/slsa-framework/slsa-github-generator/generic@v1",
    "invocation": {
      "configSource": {
        "uri": "git+https://github.com/owner/repo@refs/heads/main",
        "digest": { "sha1": "..." },
        "entryPoint": ".github/workflows/release.yml"
      }
    },
    "materials": [
      {
        "uri": "git+https://github.com/owner/repo@refs/heads/main",
        "digest": { "sha1": "..." }
      }
    ]
  }
}
                            </code></pre>
                        </div>
                        
                        <p>Untuk SLSA Build L2+, control plane menghasilkan provenance yang mendeskripsikan seluruh proses .</p>
                    </div>
                </section>

